title: Ground News - Голевой пас Цыганкова помог "Жироне" победить и сохранить второе место в Ла Лиге
text: Girona with Ukrainians Victor Cygankov and Artem Dovbyk won on their home field against Osasuna in the 28th round match of the Spanish championship. Michel's team won 2:0. In the 13th minute, Cygankov skillfully turned and made a precise pass to Christian Portu, who scored against the opponent. The second goal for the home team was scored by Savio in the late minutes of the game.
